OL,3,CSoldier attack: Were there missed
OL,4,Copportunities to stop Anthony Esan?
OL,6,FQuestions have been raised about the
OL,7,Fpossibility of missed opportunities
OL,8,Fsurrounding the mental health of a man
OL,9,Fwho repeatedly stabbed an army officer
OL,10,Fnear a barracks in Kent.
OL,12,FAnthony Esan was sentenced to life
OL,13,Fimprisonment, with a minimum term of
OL,14,Fseven years and 162 days, at Maidstone
OL,15,FCrown Court on Friday` but will be
OL,16,Fdetained in hospital for as long as
OL,17,Fnecessary ` for the knife attack on
OL,18,FLieutenant Colonel Mark Teeton in
OL,19,FSally Port Gardens, near Brompton
OL,20,FBarracks, Chatham, on July 23 2024.
