OL,3,CSoldier attack: Were there missed
OL,4,Copportunities to stop Anthony Esan?
OL,6,FEsan spent more than an hour prowling
OL,7,Fthe streets of Chatham, hunting for a
OL,8,Ftarget - a soldier in uniform.
OL,10,FMark Teeton had been walking home from
OL,11,Fhis base at Brompton Barracks, when
OL,12,FEsan asked to use his phone,
OL,13,Fdistracting him, before brutally
OL,14,Fattacking him.
OL,16,FForensic psychiatrists told Maidstone
OL,17,FCrown Court it is more likely that
OL,18,FEsan set out to stab a soldier but
OL,19,Fthat the main driver of his actions
OL,20,Fwas psychosis.
