OL,6,FDetectives later found he'd searched
OL,7,F'Woolwich Soldier Murder' - referring
OL,8,Fto the killing of Fusilier Lee Rigby
OL,9,Fby extremists.
OL,11,FThe court heard there was no single
OL,12,Fideology in his web history. The
OL,13,Fprosecution say he was simply looking
OL,14,Ffor any reason to justify what he was
OL,15,Fplanning to do.
OL,17,FIn the lead-up to the stabbing, CCTV
OL,18,Fcaptured Esan buying a set of knives
OL,19,Ffrom Argos. Later that same day, he
OL,20,Fwas given his monthly antipsychotic
OL,21,Finjection.
