OL,3,CSoldier attack: Were there missed
OL,4,Copportunities to stop Anthony Esan?
OL,6,FA month prior to the attack, Esan was
OL,7,Fdischarged from the Early Intervention
OL,8,Fin Psychosis Team, after four years of
OL,9,Ftailored support, to be treated by
OL,10,Fcommunity mental health carers.
OL,12,FThe court heard that Esan was being
OL,13,Funder-treated for schizophrenia at the
OL,14,Ftime of the attack.
OL,16,FJulian Hendy set up the charity,
OL,17,FHundred Families, after his father was
OL,18,Fmurdered by a mental health patient
OL,19,Fand said there needs to be more
OL,20,Ftransparency and assertive care.
