OL,6,FHe said: "I don't see much evidence
OL,7,Fthat mental health services are
OL,8,Factually learning from this.
OL,10,F"I know they need more money, but they
OL,11,Fneed a cultural change as well. They
OL,12,Fneed to recognise that a small number
OL,13,Fof people with serious mental illness
OL,14,Fcan be violent, and they need more
OL,15,Fassertive care and treatment.
