OL,6,F"Thank goodness, you know, the officer
OL,7,Fsurvived because I feared for quite a
OL,8,Flong time that he might not survive
OL,9,Fbecause it had all the hallmarks of a
OL,10,Fmental health related case with
OL,11,Fserious violence, and a lot of these
OL,12,Fcases should be preventable with
OL,13,Fbetter care and treatment."
OL,15,FEsan was born in Nigeria and moved to
OL,16,Fthe UK in 2009, living in the
OL,17,FSouthwark area of London before the
OL,18,Ffamily relocated to Kent in 2022.
