OL,3,CSoldier attack: Were there missed
OL,4,Copportunities to stop Anthony Esan?
OL,6,FThe court heard that Esan had made
OL,7,Fseveral unsuccessful attempts to join
OL,8,Fthe British Army in the years before
OL,9,Fhis attack, with his first application
OL,10,Fin 2020.
OL,12,FThat same year, he had been referred
OL,13,Fto mental health services as he
OL,14,Fappeared to be mentally unwell and
OL,15,Freported hearing voices.
OL,17,FThe court heard that in January 2023,
OL,18,FEsan's mother had contacted an out-of-
OL,19,Fhours service concerned that he had
OL,20,Fknives in his bag.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
