OL,3,CSoldier attack: Were there missed
OL,4,Copportunities to stop Anthony Esan?
OL,6,FExpert witness in forensic psychiatry
OL,7,FProfessor Nigel Blackwood said that
OL,8,Fwhen he brought knives back to the
OL,9,Ffamily home, that Esan "began to
OL,10,Fentertain murderous fantasies 18
OL,11,Fmonths before he enacted them".
OL,13,FProsecutor Alison Morgan KC had also
OL,14,Fsaid Esan had an "interest" in knives,
OL,15,Fwith packaging for two "Rambo" knives
OL,16,Flater to be recovered from his bedroom.
