OL,6,FSince the middle of last year Esan
OL,7,Fsaid he felt he was in the film
OL,8,FKingsman, which Ms Morgan described as
OL,9,F"profoundly violent", and a video game
OL,10,Fcalled Cyberpunk.
OL,12,FHe believed his role was to "deliver
OL,13,Fand shoot", the court heard.
OL,15,FEsan has been receiving treatment in
OL,16,FBroadmoor Hospital, but Prof Blackwood
OL,17,Fsaid he remains psychotic and will
OL,18,Fhave to be treated for the rest of his
OL,19,Flife.
